{"title":"一个孩子给我的礼物","authors":["沙蕾"],"dates":[{"year":1981,"month":4,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个孩子给我的礼物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙蕾（回族）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用微笑的花朵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佩在我的衣襟上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我变成一株春天的树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你将《晨》的画送给我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我象朝阳一样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从海面冉冉地上升。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你给我的照片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"形成了我的心影，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并时刻发出天真的歌声。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}